    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1921-07-15T21:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1921-07-15T21:00:00-05:00" n="561"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d561">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.77/2156: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Japan</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bell</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-07-16T11:00:00+09:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 16, 1921—11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received July 16—4:54 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>248. The following from Peking: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“260. July 16, 11 a.m. Your 192, July 11, 5 p.m. Cooperation promised by
                            Minister of Communication[s], bond issue abandoned for the present.
                            Despatch follows.<note n="16" xml:id="d561fn16">Not printed.</note>
                            Stevens informed.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bell</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
